text: is a former Japanese football player. She played for the Japan national team. ==Biography== Kaneda was born on March 9, 1968. She played for Shimizudaihachi SC and Nissan FC. On October 22, 1984, when Kaneda was 16 years old, she debuted for the Japan national team against Australia.
